          <li>Role-based access controls, least-privilege principles, and audit logging.</li>
          <li>Periodic security assessments, vulnerability scanning, and backups.</li>
        </ul>
        <p>While we strive to protect your data, no system is completely secure. Please help protect your account by using a strong password and keeping your login credentials private.</p>
